y of \\\"anti-Christian political and ideological persecution,\\\" the team members were reportedly jailed in \\\"gross\\\" conditions, strip-searched and prohibited from calling their lawyers or having access to water.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CitizenGo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CitizenGO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CitizenGo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CitizenGo\"}, {\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antichrist\", \"score\": 0.9929673515286581, \"rank\": 0.00707276859212895, \"text\": \"anti-Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antichrist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antichrist\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a display\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the team members\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"gross\\\" conditions\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"their lawyers\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to apress releasefrom CitizenGO founder Ignacio Arsuaga, the bus had been driving around Paris since 9 a.m. without incident until French law enforcement surrounded it and stopped it at gunpoint, arresting the six campaigners and the bus driver at around 7 p.m. Arsuaga alleged without evidence that police were dispatched to stop the bus by a French prosecutor under the orders of French President Emmanuel Macron.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2436, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CitizenGo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CitizenGO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CitizenGo\", \"dbpedia\": 